### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### ===== 步骤 1-2: 认证 =====

### Login as admin
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Login - wrong password (expect 401)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### Change password (replace <token> with actual token from login)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "oldPassword": "admin123",
  "newPassword": "newpass123"
}

### ===== 步骤 1-3: 用户管理 =====

### List Users (admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Create User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "username": "张伟",
  "password": "123456",
  "roles": ["operator"]
}

### Create Manager User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "username": "李娜",
  "password": "123456",
  "roles": ["manager"]
}

### Update User Role
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/张伟
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "roles": ["manager", "operator"]
}

### Disable User
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/张伟
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "is_active": false
}

### Delete User
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users/张伟
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### No token (expect 401)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users

### ===== 后续步骤占位 =====

### List Part Types (after step 1-4)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/part-types
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### List Inventory (after step 1-5)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/inventory?page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### KPI Summary (after step 1-7)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/analytics/kpi
Authorization: Bearer <token>
